msgstr "The handshake phase is relatively similar to the HTTP protocol. The handshake example given in the RFC is as follows:"

#: ../../source/network/http/websocket.rst:34
msgid ""
"其中 Upgrade 的值必须为 websocket ，Connection 的值必须为 Upgrade ，合起来表示客户端喜欢连接升级到 "
"Websocket 协议。"
msgstr ""
"The value of Upgrade must be websocket, and the value of Connection must "
"be Upgrade. Together, they indicate that the client wants to upgrade the "
"connection to the WebSocket protocol."

#: ../../source/network/http/websocket.rst:36
msgid ""
"Sec-WebSocket-Key 是一个随机值，Sec-WebSocket-Accept 是 Sec-WebSocket-Key 拼接特定字符串"
" ``258EAFA5-E914-47DA-95CA-C5AB0DC85B11`` 计算SHA1摘要后的 Base64 编码的值。例子中 "
"``s3pPLMBiTxaQ9kYGzzhZRbK+xOo=`` 就是 "
"``dGhlIHNhbXBsZSBub25jZQ==258EAFA5-E914-47DA-95CA-C5AB0DC85B11`` "
"对应的SHA1摘要。"
msgstr ""
"Sec-WebSocket-Key is a random value. Sec-WebSocket-Accept is the Base64-"
"encoded value of the SHA1 digest calculated after concatenating Sec-"
"WebSocket-Key with the fixed string "
"``258EAFA5-E914-47DA-95CA-C5AB0DC85B11``. In the example, "
"``s3pPLMBiTxaQ9kYGzzhZRbK+xOo=`` is the SHA1 digest corresponding to "
"``dGhlIHNhbXBsZSBub25jZQ==258EAFA5-E914-47DA-95CA-C5AB0DC85B11``."
